d for a garment, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ Τηλαύγους θ</foreign>. prob. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0673.tlg001:42\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aeschin.Socr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">42</biblScope> </bibl>: metaph., of a person, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">θ. τις λόγων</foreign> 'wind-bag', <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg006.perseus-grc1:161a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tht.\">Tht.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">161a</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τῇ χειρὶ δεῖν σπείρειν, ἀλλὰ μὴ ὅλῳ τῷ θ</foreign>. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Corinn.</author> </bibl> ap. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.348a</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n49331.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sack in which the eggs of the tunny are enveloped</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:571a:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">571a14</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:552b:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">552b19</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n49331.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in pl., slang term for the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">loose trousers</tr_> of Persians and other Orientals, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg001.perseus-grc1:182\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a><